1. *Četvrtkom* idemo na jogu. (On Thursdays we go to yoga.)
2. Danas je *četvrtak*. (Today is Thursday.)
3. *Četvrtkom* mi dolaze prijatelji u posetu. (My friends come to visit me on Thursdays.)
4. Juče smo *četvrtkom* otišli na izlet. (Yesterday we went on a trip on Thursday.)
5. Sastanak je zakazan za *četvrtak*. (The meeting is scheduled for Thursday.)
6. *Četvrtkom* obično pečem kolače. (I usually bake cakes on Thursdays.)
7. U *četvrtak ujutru* putujem za Beograd. (I am traveling to Belgrade on Thursday morning.)
8. *Četvrtak je* dan za odlazak na pijacu. (Thursday is the day to go to the market.)
9. U sredu mi je rekao da će doći u *četvrtak*. (He told me on Wednesday that he will come on Thursday.)
10. Idemo u *četvrtak naveče* na koncert. (We are going to a concert on Thursday evening.)

Note: The word "četvrtak" means "Thursday" in English.